{"tid":1696237,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[長文] 我有一個中產既黃絲老豆","createTime":"2019-11-06T05:10:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-07T08:24:01.000Z","uid":234116,"like":174,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"e9d9449aff3113a86822b9fe891a0fb3edc0de36","tid":1696237,"uid":234116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T05:10:48.000Z","msg":"大家好<br />\n係我細個既時候，我印象中既老豆已經係黃<br />\n佢係我記憶入面一直都係教主嘅信徒<br />\n我仲記得佢係我細細個就帶我去03年7.1遊行<br />\n<br />\n係今次運動入面佢都有聽我建議捐錢比星火<br />\n我係今次運動入面會標榜自己為半個勇武<br />\n基本係只有冇玩過魔法<br />\n我老豆就唔會阻止我出去，只會同我講早d返<br />\n不過佢成日同我講<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">「啊仔，我哋唔係冇選擇，我哋有錢可以移民，我哋又可以捐錢，唔晒次次都出去，去到咁前架」</span></span><br />\n我又會同佢講<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">「如果個個都係咁，冇付出既心，冇犧牲既覺悟，只係一味掛住諗自己，咁香港一定冇光復既一日」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我成日都會講多呢句「如果97前有今次三分一既人出來，一早就唔輪到我哋出來啦！」<br />\n結果我同我老豆係呢啲話題永遠都不歡而散<br />\n<br />\n前幾日我陪我老豆去食飯，跟手佢飲多左開始發酒瘋，佢一開始就會撩女仔之後就來料啦<br />\n佢望住我之後就開始喊<br />\n<br />\n「我個仔啊我個仔啊，我同媽咪都好擔心你啊！媽咪成日因為你訓唔到覺，我又成日又口掛掛擔心你出事呀！」「你成日去到咁前，你出事叫我哋點算啊！我哋唔係冇得簡架！」<br />\n<br />\n我一見佢咁我即刻攬實佢個頭(佢當時坐低左)<br />\n一來想佢冷靜啲，二來佢咁大聲怕比人篤灰<br />\n<br />\n結果我老豆大大力抱返我轉頭<br />\n之後一邊喊一邊講<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「對唔住啊仔！係我當年冇出來，搞到你而家代替我，做我應該做既野！」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n一聽到佢咁講我呆左下，之後眼睛開始泛紅<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「我同媽咪冇左你唔得架，你出事咁我地點算啊！我地真係會吊頸架！不過我一定會揾人陪葬！起碼十個！我識好多人架！我已經叫左佢地睇實架啦！」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「爸爸知你好正義，不過爸爸媽咪又點算啊！我哋冇左你真係唔得架，你真係唔好有事啊！」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n呢個時候我老豆d朋友走過來拍我膊頭，同我講「做人要自私d,你已經做咗好多啦」「你老豆真係好擔心你架，個次知你係港島走唔到，佢當堂咩心情都冇晒」<br />\n我一邊聽一邊流眼淚，我老豆一個五十幾既大男人抱住我嚎哭，又大力攬實我<br />\n<br />\n之後我哋送我老豆返去，我幫佢除衫訓覺後就返左房，我係床上面打開Facebook 見到班黑警既暴行，科大男仔危胎，義士單人引走班狗<br />\n我一邊睇一邊喊，我究竟可以點做！<br />\n我真係可以唔出聲咩？我真係可以裝聾作啞咩？<br />\n<br />\n一瞬間我真係唔知點做，香港係我屋企，但我都有一個更細既屋企<br />\n我成日都覺得，如果屋企係藍，咁我一定可以去得更盡，好似我有時會諗如果我比差佬打，我個深藍爺爺會唔會轉黃呢？<br />\n<br />\n我而家真係覺得出又唔係，唔出又唔係<br />\n做勇武好難<br />\n但係做港豬更難<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">五大訴求</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">缺一不可</span></span>"},{"pid":"d17f3df73861405c3eff8fb6740278393aae3e22","tid":1696237,"uid":68467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T05:39:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11851c9b720f619fede5796fcbb06e96badf5d64","tid":1696237,"uid":131122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T05:40:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c55ce9fc6fe462b89a29212d1dd8fe59c2873060","tid":1696237,"uid":308682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T05:40:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91c2c89aced4501185d6294d506791b4705f450d","tid":1696237,"uid":139339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T05:41:47.000Z","msg":"Support bro!"},{"pid":"356f1d3b2b35a1f0481948e1a4e2a9fcf75f4ec1","tid":1696237,"uid":67006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T05:41:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51b22185a8263897fe3f4a655b3961cd6afafb53","tid":1696237,"uid":251873,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T05:44:18.000Z","msg":"做你第日諗返唔會後悔嘅嘢啦<br />\n做父母一定擔心<br />\n出去覆多啲佢哋<br />\n起碼第時你做人老豆<br />\n唔會因為為佢做得唔夠多而難過"},{"pid":"7b64be457ea0e424eb3b7da2aeccfa4bb7fc6cc8","tid":1696237,"uid":119232,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T05:45:07.000Z","msg":"催淚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我唔想將來做你老豆既角色<br />\n一定要贏丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9ae77b1189211c5b25630c59aee3f59e5fa7c9e","tid":1696237,"uid":150053,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T05:47:37.000Z","msg":"最後果句好啱,<br />\n要做港豬更難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42067c055724578b2315ea9147826067daa0af7e","tid":1696237,"uid":9326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T05:51:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我都想有一個黃既老豆"},{"pid":"5b8bde6de895bab22bafd3f274ccaa2746a74097","tid":1696237,"uid":278015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T05:53:14.000Z","msg":"我一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da14e1f705299bb28df22a560755ce26d7b7899c","tid":1696237,"uid":78907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T05:53:16.000Z","msg":"咁講雖然好膠<br />\n但保護人嘅信念可以催化最大 甚至乎超越原本自己嘅力量"},{"pid":"0261abb5a8c0e73a4bff6a87231594c331ab2576","tid":1696237,"uid":53612,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T05:53:46.000Z","msg":"上一代無出，因為再上一代叫佢唔好出，今代唔出，因為上一代叫唔好出<br />\n<br />\n無人付出，那有進步"},{"pid":"753b6eef03c3c5dac630b0294068828ecb3c1c25","tid":1696237,"uid":200479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T05:54:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0273507ee20ecc8161d853473e8f1aaeed469be7","tid":1696237,"uid":9483,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T06:00:38.000Z","msg":"難聽講句點都要出<br />\n而一代唔出就會好似你老豆咁，害左下一代人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇你良心過唔過得去"},{"pid":"1e3e953a48448b7050935f41c5c23a3b2b18c1c3","tid":1696237,"uid":270214,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T06:35:00.000Z","msg":"所有黃絲父母見到荃灣手足浮屍<br />\n縛住對手流晒血嗰幅相<br />\n都已經嚇破膽<br />\n<br />\n係好明白佢地忠義兩難全嘅心態<br />\n但，作為一個真.手足<br />\n&lsquo;我不要毅然別去 <br />\n背城借一遠方寄居<br />\n有種愛超越限期盛衰<br />\n流在我血液身體裏<br />\n任雨打 任風吹<br />\n我也在這裏。。。。&rsquo;<br />\n<br />\n有血性嘅人會憑良心為正義而戰<br />\n但有好多崗位，好多方法<br />\n唔一定要犧牲性命<br />\n所以每一個人都要發揮自己所長去繼續抗爭<br />\n長期𡚒鬥勝算仲高<br />\n衝百次不如三罷一個月<br />\n立即被捕不如立即癱瘓<br />\n換個方法換個心態<br />\n釜底抽薪出奇制勝"},{"pid":"653258f0ecb199ff7d4960c09d51786f35f58ee5","tid":1696237,"uid":234116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T06:59:29.000Z","msg":"一諗到如果我比狗咬屋企人可能做傻事<br />\n我就好唔安樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09dbe9d48c3b4f3cb37037121989729e5116d4a7","tid":1696237,"uid":182259,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T07:22:01.000Z","msg":"佢地擔心你<br />\n但會以你為榮<br />\n養兒一百歲 長憂九十九<br />\n出街前溝通多啲 記住平安歸來"},{"pid":"551a757ad9622a2cde5aaac7bf433766ef73fb20","tid":1696237,"uid":196774,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T07:28:21.000Z","msg":"為左你屋企人<br />\n衰d講句 唔好行咁前。<br />\n萬事小心"},{"pid":"79ef80d40c7d6651977a0af1051216883f474214","tid":1696237,"uid":34336,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T08:09:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1554cf0f79edefc428c50fd82ad30e7bc54f1ec3","tid":1696237,"uid":237342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51b22185a8263897fe3f4a655b3961cd6afafb53","tid":1696237,"uid":251873,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T05:44:18.000Z","msg":"做你第日諗返唔會後悔嘅嘢啦<br />\n做父母一定擔心<br />\n出去覆多啲佢哋<br />\n起碼第時你做人老豆<br />\n唔會因為為佢做得唔夠多而難過"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T08:10:25.000Z","msg":"係 第時唔會再循環落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b44b53299fa7d5757ab72c1a097342d3a817e554","tid":1696237,"uid":234116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79ef80d40c7d6651977a0af1051216883f474214","tid":1696237,"uid":34336,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T08:09:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T08:23:08.000Z","msg":"但但如果真係咩都唔做<br />\n香港又由邊個來救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c83e7eaeeff2485e1e92f712996a362d797f0fa1","tid":1696237,"uid":234116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42067c055724578b2315ea9147826067daa0af7e","tid":1696237,"uid":9326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T05:51:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我都想有一個黃既老豆"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T08:28:48.000Z","msg":"加油啊巴打"},{"pid":"0e10ccd629d46f04bfd8e86c9c26849fd141c601","tid":1696237,"uid":272822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T08:37:55.000Z","msg":"屌你未扯旗就係度放tg <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"576277371e10bbf1b7a2bfa92016beceb01ca385","tid":1696237,"uid":34336,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T09:18:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}